sentences.sContent: Results for the test programme haven't been tabulated.
sentences.sCn: 试验项目的结果还没有制成表格。

remMethod.val: tabl (e) (表格) + ate (做…) → 做成表格 → 把…制成表格

words.tran: 制表机；作表的人；跳格键

trans.tranOther: to arrange figures or information together in a set or a list, so that they can be easily compared
